fitt1 <- bn.fit(bn.wl.bl, s1)
junction = compile(as.grain(fitt1))
## Warning in from.bn.fit.to.grain(x): NaN conditional probabilities in EVOLUCAO,
## replaced with a uniform distribution.
jedu = setEvidence(propagate = TRUE, junction,
                   node = c("CLASSI_FIN",
                            "IDADE",
                            "OBESIDADE",
                            "UTI",
                            "SUPORT_VEN"),
                   states = c("5",
                              "(36,71]",
                              "1",
                              "2",
                              "1") )
querygrain(jedu,
           nodes = c("EVOLUCAO"),
           type = "marginal")
